reviewText: Any "Porky's" fan will LOVE this!  All three movies in ONE place! We had a "Porky's" marathon and it was filled with laughter!

porkys 1 and 2 are incredibly funny and unique, porkys revenge is decent but not as funny, the story and acting are really good and it will make you laugh, follow the boys of angel beach high as they go on a quest to get some lovin at the local brothel with hillarious results.
was a great deal and worked good. it shiped fast and got to my house before i expected it  2 thumbs up

We love porky's. I had the first one and wanted the other two. I found this on Amazon and placed a fairly large order of movies. This came first out of all the items and within days of placing the order. It was a used product and it was in fair condition. I watched one movie last night, the second one, and it had a small pause in it but that can easily be buffed out. other than that, so far so good. I think I would order from these people again.

I saw all three of these movies when they where first released and probably a dozen times since and they just get better over time, if you don't already have all three then you need these. Great movies at a great price.

Porky's is one of those movies that gets funnier every time you watch it because each time you see it you catch something you missed laughing the first time. Not for children though. It has a lot of nudity and when not outright sexual language, there's sexual innuendos. I got the 3 movie pack so I'd have all 3 of the movies.
I had been "collecting" the series, one at a time when they became cheap and was happy to find a single offering with all of them (unless another is made in the future!)  Thanks for the service

I have seen all the Porky Movies Thanks to Netflix and I have on DVD Porky's 1, I can't believe there is no dvd Of Porky's 2 or Porky's 3, I would have to buy the vhs or the Ultimate Collection(All 3) on Dvd, I give the First one 5 stars, the 2nd 4 stars and the 3rd installment 3 stars. Porky's Movies never disappoint.

Funny in a classical way. These movie are from the early 1980's but are already classics. Fun stories and fun scenes. Will keep the young adult males interested and laughing.
These movies are classic comedies.  Nice to have in one package.  The sequels are not as great as the original but still funny.
Porky's one will make you laugh out loud.  The second movie is great also as is the third.  I recommend these movies to everyone.

I bought these for my husband. I seen the first one so many years ago, but watching it again and the other two was fun to watch. We especially enjoyed the commentary at the end. We had no idea that these stories were actually events that happened to other people and the way they were all brought together to make a movie was amazing..
